Privacy Policy for Hat Zad ##


Hat Zad takes your privacy seriously. To better protect your privacy, we provide this privacy policy notice explaining the way your personal information is collected and used.



Collection of Personal Information ##


 When using the Hat Zad app, we may collect personal information that you provide to us, including but not limited to:

Name and contact details (such as phone number).

Delivery address and location data to ensure accurate order fulfillment.


None of the routine technical information is used to personally identify users outside of the app's core functionality (ordering and delivery).




Cookies and Local Storage  ##


 Where necessary, the Hat Zad app uses local storage or cookies to store information about your preferences and order history in order to better serve you and present you with customized content.

Account Deletion##
To delete your account and all associated data, please contact us at [Naserrsakkaf2013@gmail.com]. We will process your request within 48 hours.

Advertisement and Other Third Parties ##


 Our app does not display third-party advertisements. However, we may use service providers to facilitate our service (such as hosting or delivery tracking). 
These third parties have access to your personal information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.

Links to Third Party Services ##


 We may include links or services in the app for your use and reference. We are not responsible for the privacy policies of these external services or websites. You should be aware that their privacy policies may differ from our own.




Payment Security Hat Zad ##


 does not process or store credit card or electronic payment data within the app. All payments are conducted externally (Cash on Delivery or Manual Bank Transfer).
While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect the personal information you provide (like your address), remember that no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.



Changes To This Privacy Policy ##


 This Privacy Policy is effective as of [1 February 2026] and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page. 
We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time.

Contact Information For any questions or concerns regarding the privacy policy, please send us an email to: [Naserrsakkaf2013@gmail.com]
